Story: Home Page

  As an anonymous user
  I want to see the home page
  So that I know what information there is
  
  Scenario: showing home page
  
    Given an anonymous user
    
    When visiting '/'
    
    Then user should see page/home


  Scenario: Seeing tools

    Given an anonymous user
    
    When visiting '/'
    And clicks on 'Errata'
    Then user should see erratas/index

    When visiting '/'
    And clicks on 'Source Code'
    Then user should see page/source
